lead_paragraph: Olympique de Marseille's dismal home form continued on Sunday when they were held 0-0 in Ligue 1 by second-from-bottom En Avant Guingamp, their fourth league draw in a row.

headline.print_headline: Marseille Draw With Guingamp in Another Home Setback
